        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-12 text-left">
                <div id="instructions-container">
                    <h2>Import New Events</h2>
                    <p id="instructions">
                        To import new events/opportunities from an external website:<br>
                        <ol>
                            <li>Install the Kimono Chrome extension.</li>
                            <li>Using Kimono, select the title, company, location and link from the opportunity list.</li>
                            <li>Specify that you want to extract the href for the link and text values for all other fields.</li>
                            <li>Generate an API for scraping the data.</li>
                            <li>Paste the API URL and the type of opportunities in the form below.</li>
                        </ol>
                    </p>
                </div>
                <form class="Import" action="http://localhost:1337/item/insert" method="POST" autocomplete="off">
                  <h3><strong>API URL</strong></h3>
                  <input class="textfield" type="text" name="url" placeholder="eg. Put API URL here">
                  <br>
                  <h3><strong>CATEGORY OF EVENT</strong></h3>
                  <input class="textfield" type="text" name="type" placeholder="eg. Internship">
                  <br><br>
                  <input type="submit" name="Submit button" value="Sumbit">
                </form>


